Subject: Server Error
Description: We attempted to log in today and received an error that stated, Oops! An Error Occurred The server returned a "500 Internal Server Error". Please e-mail us at support@endpointprotector.com and let us know what you were doing when this error occurred. We will fix it as soon as possible. Sorry for any inconvenience caused. Please let us know how to proceed as the server is currently inaccessible. Server install provided by EPP, unknown current server version or OS version.
Solution_Comment__c: We have resolved this issue by clearing space on the disk and performing some optimization regarding resource allocation. We also suggested to increases the disk space as the issue may reocurr in the future.
